      "id": "1347886090566708",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Absolutely fantastic!",
      "review_description": "I love all of it. The voice interaction is an incredible feature as well as the mixed reality. The secrets you can find are truest astonishing and require you to use your brainpower.\n\nHowever, quick question. I found the golden ring in the prison cell, and now I can’t seem to find it anywhere. I went back multiple times and searched in the wall, but it never reappeared. I tried spawning it with my voice and looking all over my desk, but it never showed up. Thoughts? Is this a glitch or intentional?",
      "date": 1780260869,
      "review_helpful_count": 21,
      "author_display_name": "turtlelibrary",
      "author_alias": "turtlelibrary",
      "developer_response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "1150622978139357",
      "score": 3,
      "review_title": "Kinda meh",
      "review_description": "I won't lie, I'm the type of person who only has 2 go-to games—Roblox and Minecraft (with mods, of course). I play very little because I'm disinterested; I've played RDR, COD, some indie games, etc.\nThis game is honestly not bad; it's alright. The reason it gets three stars is that it gets boring really quickly (for me personally). People make it seem fun on TikTok, but I just got so bored. I like the skulls' voicelines tho ig 🫩",
